Package: kernel-proc-lab
Architecture: any
Depends: dkms, kmod, make, gcc, sudo, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Linux kernel module lab with procfs, ioctl, and TUI tooling
 Kernel Proc Lab is an educational out-of-tree Linux kernel module project.
 It includes a character device, procfs/sysfs/debugfs interfaces, ioctl ABI,
 a retained event ring, pollable streams, command-line tooling, a terminal
 monitor, collector service templates, and DKMS packaging support.
